====Usage note====
In formal writing, ''Юта'' and other U.S. state names are used such that they do not decline, as demonstrated in the following quotation:
:В штате Юта совершила посадку капсула с кометным веществом &mdash; [http://www.utro.ru/news/2006/01/15/512586.shtml Эхо Москвы], January 15, 2006.

